      "rationale": "Validation activities were conducted exclusively under steady-state inflow conditions. The COU specifies pulsatile flow representative of cardiopulmonary bypass (60–80 bpm, 70 mL stroke volume). No pulsatile experimental dataset was used as comparator. The assessment team asserted that steady-state conditions bound worst-case shear exposure; however, this assertion was not supported by a formal similarity analysis or sensitivity study. Achieved level is 1, below the required level of 2 for MRL 2. This gap was noted in the assessment but was not escalated as a disqualifying finding, which constitutes the primary inference-method mismatch (D3 undercutting) embedded in this package.",
